These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, dahlia, poppy
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, spy, superhero
House: colonial, futuristic, victorian
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, car, motorbike
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the victorian house##1
2. the colonial house is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person who growslily is between the person watching spy movies and the person watching superhero movies##2
4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
5. the victorian house is the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Flower         | dahlia | lily   | poppy   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | disaster | superhero |
| House   | victorian  | colonial    | futuristic      |
| Transport     | car     | bus      | motorbike |

