.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
There 3 different types of food: kale, raspberry, tomato
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, bongani, oliveros
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, japanese, pakistani
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, daisy, zinnia
1. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
2. the pakistani is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
3. the person eating raspberry is the pakistani##1
4. the person eating kale is the japanese##1
5. the person who growspoppy is between the bongani-smoker and the person eating tomato##2
6. the person eating tomato is the person who growsdaisy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Food          | raspberry  | kale     | tomato     |
| Cigar   | bongani     | oliveros     | old-henry      |
| Nationality   | pakistani  | japanese | australian |
| Flower           | zinnia | poppy     | daisy       |

