.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, kale, orange
There are 3 different favourite colors: aquamarine, blood-red, ebony
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, july, january
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, snake
1. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is between the person who likes ebony and the person who's birthday is in january##2
3. the person eating eggplant is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is the person eating kale##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Food          | eggplant  | orange     | kale     |
| Color           | ebony | aquamarine  | blood-red   |
| Birthday   | april  | july    | january |
| Pet           | snake     | chinchilla | goldfish |

