.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: dancing, traveling, sudoku
The people have 3 different jobs:  journalist, paramedic, scientist
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: tulip, azalea, bellflower
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, rugby, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the scientist##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is between the paramedic and the person who growstulip##2
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Hobby    | dancing       | sudoku  | traveling   |
| Job     | paramedic    | scientist  | journalist |
| Flower     | azalea   | bellflower | tulip        |
| Sport   | snowboarding | rowing     | rugby      |

