.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-5::.
There 3 different types of food: carrot, cherry, plum
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, filmmaking, photography
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, handball, surfing
City: berlin, nizza, hamburg
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
2. the person traveling to berlin is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person who's hobby is photography##2
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person traveling to nizza##1
4. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person eating plum##1
5. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person eating cherry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Food          | plum    | carrot     | cherry      |
| Hobby         | cooking | filmmaking | photography |
| Sport   | surfing  | handball       | cricket       |
| City           | nizza     | berlin       | hamburg     |

