.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-6::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, august, march
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, skydiving, sudoku
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, tennis, swimming
3 different pets are kept: fish, horse, mouse
1. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is between the person who's birthday is in august and the owner of the horse##2
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far right##1
5. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
| Birthday          | august | october | march    |
| Hobby         | skydiving | sudoku      | filmmaking |
| Sport   | climbing   | tennis     | swimming        |
| Pet           | fish      | mouse       | horse      |

