.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-7::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  nurse, bartender, journalist
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, fishing, skydiving
There are 3 different favourite colors: brown, purple, coral
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, roller, van
1. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the journalist and the person driving the car##2
3. the person who likes purple is on the right of the bartender##1
4. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person who likes brown##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |
| Job          | journalist      | bartender   | nurse |
| Hobby         | board-games | fishing | skydiving |
| Color   | brown      | coral | purple   |
| Transport     | van         | roller  | car       |

