2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
4. the architect is between the tiparillo-smoker and the person drinking water##2
5. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3      |
