2. the person eating peas is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
3. the oliveros-smoker is on the far left##1
4. the person eating papaya is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
6. the person driving the bike is the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |    3     |
| Cigar      | oliveros      | chaman | old-henry     |
