The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, balloon-flower, daffodil
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the person traveling to nizza is between the person traveling to rome and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
3. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person traveling to hamburg##1
5. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
6. the person who growsiris is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |        2        |    3     |
| Hobby       | drawing       | traveling       | chess    |
| City         | hamburg | nizza | rome |
| Sport       | lacrosse      | sailing         | handball |
| Flower   | iris        | daffodil            | balloon-flower  |

