3. the person eating cherry is in the middle##1
4. the person eating cherry is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
5. the person traveling to london is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
