2. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
3. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
4. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
5. the person eating garlic is the person watching disaster movies##1
6. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |       3       |
| Hobby      | video-games    | writing          | board-games |
| Food          | raspberry | lime           | garlic        |
| Color           | green | lilac | light-blue         |
| Movie-Genre   | action    | time-travel    | disaster      |

