.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-16::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: jazz, indie, funk
3 different pets are kept: horse, mouse, rat
House: futuristic, farmhouse, ranch-style
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, train, tram
1. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person driving the train##1
2. the owner of the rat is between the person driving the boat and the owner of the horse##2
3. the fan of funk is on the far left##1
4. the farmhouse house is the person driving the boat##1
5. the ranch-style house is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
6. the fan of jazz is on the left of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |      3       |
| Music-Genre       | funk | jazz | indie |
| Pet         | horse   | rat       | mouse        |
| House       | ranch-style | futuristic   | farmhouse         |
| Transport   | tram    | train     | boat         |

