3. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person traveling to new-york##1
4. the person traveling to nizza is the person who's hobby is baking##1
5. the person driving the airplane is the person traveling to colone##1
6. the egyptian is on the right of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |
| Hobby   | gardening | baking  | magic-tricks     |
| Nationality   | turkish    | german | egyptian |
| City           | new-york        | nizza   | colone  |
| Transport     | train      | ship   | airplane |

