The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, sports, thriller
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, folk, salsa
The people have 3 different hobbies: video-games, woodworking, reading
1. the fan of salsa is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
3. the person watching thriller movies is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
4. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
5. the person watching epic movies is on the far right##1
6. the oliveros-smoker is between the cain-smoker and the fan of folk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |
| Cigar           | tiparillo   | oliveros   | cain |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | sports   | epic     |
| Music-Genre   | folk     | d&b      | salsa    |
| Hobby           | video-games | woodworking | reading    |

