.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-19::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, mirinda
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, video-games, woodworking
There 3 different types of food: peach, pineapple, apricot
There are 3 different favourite colors: orange, white, ebony
1. the person who likes white is the person eating apricot##1
2. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
3. the person eating peach is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
4. the person eating pineapple is the person who likes ebony##1
5. the person who likes orange is between the person drinking milk and the person eating pineapple##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | mirinda     | milk        |
| Hobby         | video-games   | woodworking | board-games |
| Food   | pineapple        | peach       | apricot      |
| Color           | ebony           | orange    | white       |

