.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
There 3 different types of food: raspberry, spinach, strawberry
3 different pets are kept: dog, goldfish, rabbit
There are 3 different favourite colors: white, yellow, pink
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: r&b, metal, electronic
1. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is the fan of r&b##1
3. the person who likes yellow is the fan of r&b##1
4. the person who likes white is the person eating strawberry##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is between the fan of electronic and the person who likes yellow##2
6. the person who likes pink is the person eating raspberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Food        | spinach      | raspberry | strawberry |
| Pet         | goldfish     | rabbit    | dog        |
| Color       | yellow | pink   | white   |
| Music-Genre   | r&b          | metal     | electronic       |

 